These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter, motorbike
City: san-francisco, venice, hannover
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to venice is the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski | helicopter |
| City    | venice    | hannover | san-francisco |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, lily, bellflower
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, reggae, disco
1. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1
2. the fan of reggae is in an even position##4
3. the fan of disco is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
4. the fan of reggae is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Flower       | lily | bellflower | azalea |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | reggae     | country        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, game, dunhill
There are 3 different favourite colors: grey, ivory, coral
1. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person who likes grey##1
2. the person who likes ivory is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
3. the game-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Cigar         | dunhill     | game | baccarat |
| Color   | ivory | grey     | coral  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, modern
There 3 different types of food: peach, radish, kiwi
1. the gothic-revival house is the person eating radish##1
2. the art-deco house is the person eating kiwi##1
3. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| House   | modern | gothic-revival  | art-deco  |
| Food         | peach  | radish | kiwi |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, tulip
There 3 different types of food: grapefruit, spinach, pear
1. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsorchid and the person eating grapefruit##2
2. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Flower         | orchid   | tulip | rose    |
| Food   | spinach | pear     | grapefruit |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, light-blue, ebony
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose, begonia
1. the person who likes blood-red is the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is the person who likes light-blue##1
3. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Color   | light-blue | ebony | blood-red   |
| Flower   | begonia     | marigold    | rose |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: lavender, blue, pink
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, may, june
1. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
2. the person who likes lavender is between the person who's birthday is in june and the person who likes pink##2
3. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
4. the person who's birthday is in august is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Color   | pink | lavender | blue |
| Birthday           | may         | august         | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different games are played: poker, scrabble, domino
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, lemonade, sprite
1. the person drinking water is between the person drinking lemonade and the person playing poker##2
2. the person drinking sprite is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Game   | scrabble | domino | poker |
| Beverage    | lemonade    | water | sprite     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
House: cottage, modern, palace
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, american, russian
1. the russian is in an odd position##4
2. the american is on the left of the cottage house##1
3. the russian is on the left of the modern house##1
4. the russian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| House   | palace   | modern  | cottage  |
| Nationality         | russian | american | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, manager, electrician
3 different games are played: go, poker, domino
1. the person playing go is on the right of the electrician##1
2. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
3. the person playing domino is on the right of the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Job   | engineer    | electrician      | manager |
| Game       | poker | domino | go   |

