.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, crime, scientific
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: jazz, techno, house
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the fan of jazz is the person watching action movies##1
3. the fan of house is the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Movie-Genre         | crime | scientific | action |
| Music-Genre   | techno | house   | jazz |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daffodil, poppy
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, board-games, camping
