2. the person who growssunflower is the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
4. the person who's hobby is camping is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Flower   | poppy | daffodil | sunflower |
| Hobby     | board-games     | hiking   | camping        |

