.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, blues, soul
There are 3 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, pink
1. the fan of soul is between the fan of blues and the person who likes ivory##2
2. the fan of blues is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
4. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | soul | folk |
| Color     | fuchsia    | pink  | ivory   |

