2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the snake##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Color          | emerald | white | purple  |
| Pet   | pony      | guinea-pig  | snake |

