2. the person who growsbellflower is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Flower      | bellflower | zinnia | balloon-flower |
