.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, baking, writing
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, train, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Hobby     | baking  | writing   | singing |
| Transport   | airplane | train | motorbike       |

 